{"tid":330552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本腦炎】全球首宗！男病人因輸血中招危殆 留院瑪麗","createTime":"2017-07-21T10:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T10:22:18.000Z","uid":15440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7550022a98e83fff1ffdd70ac3132f0ef3e39c90","tid":330552,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:12:34.000Z","msg":"【日本腦炎】全球首宗！男病人因輸血中招危殆 留院瑪麗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名5月初於瑪麗醫院接受換肺的52歲男病人，同月轉到葛量洪醫院留醫；直至本月6日接受輸血後，出現發燒及神志不清等病徵，昨日證實感染日本腦炎，情況危殆，現留醫瑪麗醫院心胸外科。據了解，紅十字會已驗出輸予該病人的血液中，有一包血液有日本腦炎病毒，而有關的捐血人士其實也有捐出血小板、血漿，紅十字會仍會追蹤相關血小板、血漿的去向。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總感染控制主任曾艾壯昨表示，文獻沒有記載透過輸血或器官移植感染日本腦炎的病例，但理論上有風險。因此，此個案相信是全球首宗。<br />\n<br />\n防護中心昨表示，日本腦炎主要經蚊傳播，海外有科學文獻顯示，其他類似黃病毒，輸血和器官移植也可能傳播日本腦炎病毒。按現階段掌握病人的臨床紀錄及接觸史，仍需繼續流行病學調查，以盡量確認感染源頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170721&amp;guid=56985042&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170721%26guid%3D56985042%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=lQxHVXYVGApsbYdR3oXkxjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d71881ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170721%26guid%3D56985042%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=009917cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170721&amp;guid=56985042&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"411d8a0d52a2d3e7e97d16ab34e10be5662a7a98","tid":330552,"uid":23836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128392d68a94be7e582cb666aa518755c71e061f","tid":330552,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}